They were immediately distracted by the bronze statue of a calf in the courtyard!

[caption id="attachment_646" align="alignleft" width="375"]<a href="http://www.dayofarchaeology.com/the-star-carr-project-gets-visitors/alicerandcalf/" rel="attachment wp-att-646"><img class="size-medium wp-image-646 " title="AliceRandCalf" alt="Alice Roberts and the King's Manor Calf Statue" src="http://www.dayofarchaeology.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/AliceRandCalf-375x500.jpg" width="375" height="500" /></a> Alice Roberts and the King's Manor Calf Statue (via @GemmaHagen360)[/caption]

