My name is Colm Moloney and I am the Managing Director of Headland Archaeology (Ireland) Ltd. We are one of the larger commercial archaeological companies operating in Ireland.

&nbsp;

[caption id="attachment_1387" align="alignnone" width="240" caption="The office of Headland Archaeology (Ireland) Ltd on Little Island in County Cork"]<a href="http://www.dayofarchaeology.com/a-day-in-the-life-of-an-irish-managing-director-archaeologist/cork-office/" rel="attachment wp-att-1387"><img class="size-full wp-image-1387" title="Cork Office" src="http://www.dayofarchaeology.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/Cork-Office.jpg" alt="" width="240" height="320" /></a>[/caption]

