[caption id="attachment_1386" align="alignnone" width="373" caption="A complete and intact Bronze Age pot delivered to the office today"]<a href="http://www.dayofarchaeology.com/a-day-in-the-life-of-an-irish-managing-director-archaeologist/pot-2/" rel="attachment wp-att-1386"><img class="size-medium wp-image-1386" title="Pot" src="http://www.dayofarchaeology.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/Pot1-373x500.jpg" alt="" width="373" height="500" /></a>[/caption]

