&nbsp;

[caption id="attachment_1446" align="alignnone" width="580" caption="Heading to work"]<a href="http://www.dayofarchaeology.com/up-the-hill/hill2/" rel="attachment wp-att-1446"><img class="size-medium wp-image-1446" title="hill2" src="http://www.dayofarchaeology.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/hill2-580x435.jpg" alt="Heading to work" width="580" height="435" /></a>[/caption]

